data.description: Totally Rebuilt first and second floor in 2022, Large six-bedrooms 4 Bath two story home located on a private lot in Parkland School District. Huge Eat in Kitchen, Dining room, Living room w/fireplace and three spacious Bedrooms one of which is a Master on the first floor as well as two full baths, one of which is in the Master Bedroom. The second floor has three Bedrooms one of which is a Master bedroom with a Master bath. Also, a Jack and Jill bath. The home has a four-car garage and a semi-finished basement with a wood burning stove. The property is located on a 1.3-acre lot at the end of a long lane. Enjoy the neighboring Vinyard and privacy.
